**Describe the bug**

```
23:41:11.360 [pulsar-client-io-1-1:org.apache.pulsar.client.impl.ProducerImpl@271] ERROR org.apache.pulsar.client.impl.ProducerImpl - Semaphore permit release count request greater then availablePermits : availablePermits=350, releaseCountRequest=380
